value.name: Manhunt: The Search for America's Most Gorgeous Male Model
value.original_name: Manhunt: The Search for America's Most Gorgeous Male Model
value.overview: A reality television series following a formula similar to UPN/The CW's America's Next Top Model, but with two differences. One, all the contestants are male, and two, there is a spy among the men. Also, multiple contenders are voted off each time, unlike the single-elimination structure of America's Next Top Model.
